{"tid":499592,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"點解譚仔一個餸嘅份量會多過兩個餸？","createTime":"2017-12-15T03:54:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T13:36:58.000Z","uid":6031,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d1b7238197488656898ee15b444e8c323b5807a6","tid":499592,"uid":6031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:54:38.000Z","msg":"叫兩個餸，例如：<br />\n我叫炸醬牛肉，炸醬黎到得三分一碗，牛肉會得4-5舊<br />\n<br />\n但如果我叫一個餸，例如：<br />\n炸醬米線，炸醬會有半碗滿<br />\n牛肉米線，牛肉會有7舊<br />\n<br />\n但餸錢都係同價<br />\n<br />\n叫三個餸係咪每樣餸嘅份量都會再少啲？<br />\n但我係俾三個餸嘅錢喎，咁咪好蝕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e13c932dd1b7cb63803ed6828206c9addf15aaf","tid":499592,"uid":58552,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:55:45.000Z","msg":"高式卡 ce econ"},{"pid":"5355ae0053afc0894178c9805dc0820899f19cac","tid":499592,"uid":114064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T04:01:15.000Z","msg":"劫富濟貧"},{"pid":"580da4a0f0d776e8f56d61da7a178bac44f6731c","tid":499592,"uid":23087,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T04:01:57.000Z","msg":"因為佢on9"},{"pid":"f3a66d948996db4234b01d8b6f984373d57b0ceb","tid":499592,"uid":6031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T04:08:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高式卡 ce econ</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5272a33fc7c3be6f24870072d114d6f4ceae9b8","tid":499592,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T04:09:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高式卡 ce econ</blockquote><br />\n有親呢d問題都諗起呢條片"},{"pid":"5ebc8b581fef19aba640f895c0bb5f913f88cf7f","tid":499592,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T04:10:42.000Z","msg":"讀得書少真係睇得出"},{"pid":"7a9b595d4e35fb8f47093f1b32d3574f0ffd645b","tid":4